data.description: This spacious 3 bedroom/2 bath home situated on 4.68 acres in the desirable Shady Oak Subdivision boast many amenities.  The large  living room features beautiful wood beams and plenty of room for entertaining guest. The roomy kitchen can be the centerpiece where you gather with family and friends, cooking and enjoying meals together. The home has 2 hot water heaters, large closets, a walk in shower, and garden tub, offering ample space and comfort.  The property also includes a huge 1200 sq/ft. metal shop with additional covered parking, convenient for storing tools and equipment.  There is even an RV shed with electricity and an outdoor guest room, making it the ideal place to host visitors.  With it's scenic location and ample space, this home is the perfect place for those seeking a peaceful and comfortable lifestyle in the heart of Shady Oaks.
